# Integration Rules

## Purpose
Ensure stable integrations with external services.

## Allowed Integrations

Examples:

- news APIs
- NGO registries
- sanctions datasets
- OSINT feeds
- domain registries

## Data Normalization

All external data must transform into:


Signal Object


Schema:


signal_id
timestamp
source
text
entities
confidence


## Error Handling

All integrations must implement:

- retry logic
- rate limit handling
- structured logging

Retries must use exponential backoff.

## Execution Window

Integration services run:
before ingestion processing begins.